Get Glue WP is a plugin to show your stats (most recent checkin, # of checkin, etc) from Get Glue
on your Wordpress blog.

It uses OAuth to authenticate you, and has a widget that you will need to add.

If you have questions or feedback, email plugins@mitchellhislop.com, or
contact me via [mitchellhislop.com](http://mitchellhislop.com)
